text: Laia Pérez Guasch (born 4 March 1993) is an Andorran footballer who plays as a midfielder. She has been a member of the Andorra women's national team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Andorran women's footballers Category:Andorra women's international footballers
